text: Eleonora Goldoni (Finale Emilia, born 16 February 1996) is an Italian footballer who plays as a forward for Napoli in the Serie A and has appeared for the Italy women's national team. ==Career== Goldoni has been capped for the Italy national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Italian women's footballers Category:Italy women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:East Tennessee State Buccaneers women's soccer players
